  "title": "a saggy bending...",
  "sourceFile": "Burbank_notes/bentknee_N.htm",
  "encoding": "windows-1252",
  "html": "\n<div><center>\n<table>\n<tr>\n<td><font><img src=\"../images/R.gif\"/> <strong>a saggy\n        bending...</strong></font><hr noshade=\"\"/>\n<p><font>Symbolises humility. Cf. Dante,\n        Purgatory I.51: \" My guide, then laying hold on me,\n        by words / And intimations given with hand and head, /\n        Made my bent knees and eye submissive pay / Due\n        reverence.\" Saggy colours the representation\n        slightly negatively.</font></p>\n<p><font><em>reference topics</em></font></p>\n<table>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"Purgatory_I_DA.htm\">Purgatory, Canto I</a></td>\n<td><a href=\"Purgatory_I_DA.htm\"><font><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></font></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Dante and Bleistein</td>\n<td><a href=\"Burbank.htm\"><font><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></font></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Bleistein and Misrepresentation</td>\n<td><a href=\"Burbank.htm\"><font><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></font></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Burbank and Bleistein</td>\n<td><a href=\"Burbank.htm\"><font><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></font></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"Burbank_A.htm\"><font>back to \"Burbank\"</font></a></td>\n<td><a href=\"Burbank_A.htm\"><font><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></font></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</center></div>\n",
  "text": "a saggy bending... Symbolises humility. Cf. Dante, Purgatory I.51: \" My guide, then laying hold on me, by words / And intimations given with hand and head, / Made my bent knees and eye submissive pay / Due reverence.\" Saggy colours the representation slightly negatively. reference topics Purgatory, Canto I Dante and Bleistein Bleistein and Misrepresentation Burbank and Bleistein back to \"Burbank\"",
